listing_description:
['Overseen by Mummy Mountain’s purple peaks and surrounded by the splendor of the Sonoran Desert, the sprawling Scottsdale Plaza Resort & Villas is the laid-back AZ resort to gather, commune, relax, and get happy.

Attractions await you: 
✔Largest indoor butterfly sanctuary in US, Butterfly Wonderland
✔World-class hiking and rock climbing at Camelback Mountain
✔Wild West atmosphere at Cave Creek
✔Golf courses nearby
✔Large collection of agave and cacti at Desert Botanical GardenThe spaceFeaturing two queen-size beds, comfy chair and ottoman, and private exterior-facing ground floor or second-level entrances, the Deluxe Double Guest Room is among the more spacious standard accommodations in Scottsdale. It includes complimentary WiFi, writing desk and chair, mini refrigerator, charging docks, coffee maker compatible with all Keurig® and other pod beverages, barn-door bath entrance, walk-in shower, granite vanity, bathrobes, iron and ironing board, and in-room safe — plus a microwave is also available upon request. Enjoy a great stay in this Deluxe Double guest room at Scottsdale Plaza & Villas.

✔ Two Queen Beds
✔ 370 – 380 SQ/FT
✔ Suitable for 4 guests
✔ Perfect for families
✔ Bathrobes
✔ Mini refrigerator
✔ K-cup compatible coffee maker
✔ Flat-screen TV
✔ Safe

And there is more, the property offers some amazing features like:
✔  Fitness center
✔  5 outdoor pools
✔  SpaGuest access24/7 coverage service prepared to welcome youOther things to note▶ Mandatory fees
—  An incidental deposit of $60 per night is required at arrival. This will be collected by credit card. You should be reimbursed within 7 days of check-out. Your deposit will be refunded in full by credit card, subject to an inspection of the property.

▶ Optional fees
—  We allow pets: Each guest room may have a pet that does not exceed 50 pounds. The guest will be required to pay a $75 non-refundable pet cleaning fee per room.

▶ Special features 
—  Fitness center
—  5 outdoor pools
—  Business center
—  Salon and spa - Additional charges may apply
—  Tennis Courts

▶ Arriving/Leaving
—  Check-in starts at 4:00 pm
—  Check-out until 11:00 am

▶ Parking
— Free on site parking available (included in resort fee)

▶ What to do
—  See the largest indoor butterfly sanctuary in America, complete with a state-of-the-art atrium that mimics their natural habitat, at Butterfly Wonderland
—  Visit one of the most prominent outdoor destinations in Arizona. With world-class hiking and rock climbing, Camelback Mountain offers unparalleled recreational options
—  Go back in time to the Wild West by visiting Cave Creek. It boasts old-style saloons and distilleries, along with other cowboy-themed attractions for the whole family
—  Dine at great local restaurants
—  Admire a large collection of agave and cacti and over 21,000 plants at Desert Botanical Garden
—  Shop at the largest mall in the American Southwest, Fashion Square Mall
—  Learn about American Indian and their heritage at The Heard Museum

▶ Food and drink
—  On-site restaurant
—  Room service 

▶ Services
—  Reception 
—  Express check-in/check-out

I enjoy checking guests in but may not always be able to do so. I am quick to respond, let me know what you need!', "Welcome to the Papago Motor Hotel! Nestled in this vibrant and picturesque city, our hotel rooms offer everything you need for a comfortable and memorable stay. Positioned near the heart of Old Town Scottsdale, Downtown Tempe, and Phoenix, you have easy access to premier shopping, rooftop bars. Within a mere five-minute drive, explore the wonders of the Desert Botanical Garden, Papago Park, and Phoenix Zoo.The spaceOur spacious and airy rooms are thoughtfully designed to promote rest and relaxation. Featuring one plush king bed with crisp white linens. The room's large windows invites natural light to brighten your stay. 
The room is thoughtfully equipped with modern amenities, including air conditioning, to keep you cool in the Arizona sun.

Bring your beloved pets along for the adventure! Papago Motor Hotel is pet friendly and welcomes your pets at no extra charge, ensuring a comfortable and enjoyable stay for the whole family.

You'll have the convenience of a private bathroom, where you can freshen up with ease. The bathroom is clean, well-maintained, and stocked with essentials to make your stay hassle-free.

Need some downtime? Kick back and enjoy your favorite shows or movies on the flat-screen TV. For your refreshments and snacks, there's a convenient mini-fridge at your disposal, perfect for keeping drinks and leftovers chilled during your stay.

While you'll love your retreat, the true gems of this listing are the fantastic resort-style amenities available to you. Take a dip in the shared pool, perfect for soaking up the Arizona sun and making a splash on warm days. If you're looking to stay active, the shared fitness center is equipped with state-of-the-art equipment to help you keep up with your workout routine.

Start your day right with our complimentary gourmet breakfast. From Tuesday to Sunday, indulge in our 'Hidden Gem' menu featuring a variety of options like seasonal fresh fruit, creamy Siggi's vanilla yogurt, and savory egg salad sandwiches. On Mondays, enjoy our special continental breakfast. Complete your morning with a freshly brewed cup of aromatic coffee.

Enhance your stay with two exceptional dining experiences steps from your room. Hidden Gem offers coffee, cocktails, and Japanese-inspired breakfast. For dinner, Hai Noon features Japanese cuisine by James Beard award-winning chef Nobuo Fukuda, craft cocktails, and late-night bites. While not hotel-affiliated, these restaurants add culinary excellence to your stay. Check their websites for menus and reservations.

As a special thank you for booking a two-night stay, you'll receive a $25 food credit for your next order. Whether you're craving a hearty meal or a sweet treat, this credit is our way of showing appreciation for being a valued guest. Don’t miss out – book your stay today and savor the flavors!

Book your stay with us today, and experience the perfect blend of relaxation and adventure in this inviting hotel room. We can't wait to host you in the heart of Scottsdale, Arizona, and make your stay an unforgettable one!Guest accessDear guests, you have access to your private room.
